title: North Las Vegas celebrates renovation of Joe Kneip Park
text:
Published By: Las Vegas Local - Today 
Mariachis, folkloric dancers and an Elvis impersonator kicked off the grand re-opening of Joe Kneip Park in North Las Vegas on Sept. 17....
